webpackJsonp([0xf98530886f8e],{801:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>One of the most important elements of running a successful bug bounty program, is ensuring you get high quality reports. Report templates help to ensure that hackers provide you with all of the information you need to verify and validate the report.</p>\n<p>Instead of the report submission form being an empty white box where the hacker has to remember to submit the right details, a report template can prompt them with the details you need.</p>\n<p>With report templates, you create a Markdown powered template, and when a hacker submits a new report, the template is pre-loaded, which can then request certain types of information.</p>\n<h3>Adding or Editing a Report Template</h3>\n<p>To add or edit a report template:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Go to your <strong>Program Settings > Program > Customization > Submit Report Form</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><em>(Optional)</em> Choose a sample template in the <strong>Sample Templates</strong> tab of the <strong>Report Templates</strong> section.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-3b757.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 92.83489096573209%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-template-1"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-67829.png 125w,\n/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/report-template-1-c68e069685594ec0b884c9ca0eac8f3d-3b757.png 1284w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Write up a new template or edit a sample template in the <strong>Write</strong> tab.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-e276b.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 87.13629402756507%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-template-2"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-67829.png 125w,\n/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/report-template-2-0fbae3c748d30320edbd4acc0dca9a6f-e276b.png 1306w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Click the <strong>Update introduction and template</strong> button.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Result</h3>\n<p>Hackers submitting reports to your program will then be greeted with a pre-populated Issue information box, assuming no report draft has previously been saved.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-8b9af.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 68.96135265700482%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-template-3"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-67829.png 125w,\n/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-b3ac4.png 1500w,\n/static/report-template-3-25ab25584d343b3c1ed0c6fee6071b4e-8b9af.png 1656w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>',frontmatter:{path:"/programs/report-templates.html",id:"programs/report-templates",title:"Report Templates",description:null}}},pathContext:{}}}});
